title: Stephen Wolfram, The Theory of Everything , and the Gift of the Layer of Computational Reducibility
description:
Wolfram's website contains all of his research docs and summaries and visuals, so if you want to get involved in thinking about the fundamental Theory of Everything, dive right in, but first, subscribe to my channel and give it a like:-)

Wolfram's Theory of Everything
Wolfram Physics Project, visual summary https://www.wolframphysics.org/visual-summary/

Bishop Barron on The Cataclysm Sentence
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mL6ZI4KHqMc

A Psycho-ontological Analysis of Genesis
Paper submitted to Dr. Jordan B. Peterson, 2007

C. S. Lewis' Great War with Owen Barfield by Lionel Adey

Michael on Twitter: @Michael21
Karen on Twitter: @klwong43
https://karenwongart.com
https://TheMeaningCode.com

Karen's conversations with Paul VanderKlay
1) Theory of Structure
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HlMgGkwWUNY&t=103s
2) Life Story
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZC03aNsPHOQ&t=1576s
